{"tid":184224,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人真係好識利用從眾心理減低罪惡感","createTime":"2017-04-02T15:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T16:00:57.000Z","uid":93917,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"874a5bf120c307d8205e0ba4b06956fa348842c7","tid":184224,"uid":93917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:56:29.000Z","msg":"近排聽得最多嘅一句：<br />\n「關心乜乜乜黎做乜啊，香港人聽朝咪又係繼續返工返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」<br />\n<br />\n其實根本係講番俾自己聽，為自己聽朝繼續返工返學可以少啲罪惡感而講<br />\n<br />\n講青少年自殺問題又好，講香港到底比唔比得上台灣嘅時候又好<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母都總會有人衝出黎講呢句<br />\n<br />\n其實，本來就冇呢一班所謂既仆街「香港人」<br />\n<br />\n你哋自己F F左一班冷漠嘅香港人出嚟，然後扮曬跟大隊冇錯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可唔可以由自己做起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783f56c5e36e2df734a0d72c3b63a8acfdebe003","tid":184224,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:57:54.000Z","msg":"關心乜乜乜黎做乜啊，聽朝咪又係繼續返工返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652c87bd7c1dc5d82683fc2554ac0767f8eb7b0c","tid":184224,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:00:04.000Z","msg":"犬儒囉<br />\n疊馬囉<br />\n威囉"},{"pid":"e4aeb4cf527fd933348096ea0bcd8c9e71d73893","tid":184224,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:00:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我哋自己FF左一班冷漠嘅香港人出嚟，然後扮曬跟大隊冇錯咁 </span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}